# [[綠柱石|綠柱石]]
# [[錫|錫渣]]

希德洛發展公司（{{lang-en|Sideral Development}}）為鳳凰金屬公司的主要客戶，負責為其購買礦物提供資金。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/Rwanda/Business/Boost-as-Phoenix-Metal-resumes-smelting-tin/1433224-2563142-e0tbbc/index.html|title=Boost as Phoenix Metal resumes smelting tin|date=2014-12-19|publisher=The East African|access-date=2020-10-18|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021112354/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/Rwanda/Business/Boost-as-Phoenix-Metal-resumes-smelting-tin/1433224-2563142-e0tbbc/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

